### 12. `FIFO_SIZE` Modulo — Replace with Power-of-2 Mask

`FIFO_SIZE` is already 16384 (2¹⁴), so `% FIFO_SIZE` can be replaced with `& (FIFO_SIZE-1)`:

```c
#define FIFO_MASK (FIFO_SIZE - 1)

// Before:
int next = (h + 1) % FIFO_SIZE;

// After (1 cycle vs ~20 cycles on Broadway):
int next = (h + 1) & FIFO_MASK;
```

